OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 01 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1999FBBC Knowledge begins
OL,7,Fbroadcasting on digital platforms.
OL,8,
OL,9,FIt offers a mix of educational
OL,10,Fprogrammes and documentaries.
OL,11,
OL,12,FWhen the BBC's digital programme was
OL,13,Flaunched at Television Centre in London
OL,14,Fby director-general Sir John Birt on
OL,15,F21st September 1998, the planned
OL,16,Feducation and information channel was
OL,17,Freferred to as BBC Learning.
OL,18,
OL,19,FBBC Knowledge closed on 2nd March 2002
OL,20,Fand was replaced by BBC Four.
OL,21,
